                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">Usability Improvements:</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600">
                        <li><strong>Clearer Visual Hierarchy:</strong> Improved typography and spacing to guide users through content</li>
                        <li><strong>Strategic Calls-to-Action:</strong> More prominent and strategically placed CTAs</li>
                        <li><strong>Mobile-First Approach:</strong> Fully responsive design for all screen sizes</li>
                        <li><strong>Enhanced Navigation:</strong> Simplified and more intuitive menu structure</li>
                        <li><strong>Loading Performance:</strong> Optimized layout and assets for faster loading</li>
                        <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Better color contrast and semantic HTML structure</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">Aesthetic Enhancements:</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600">
                        <li><strong>Modern Color Scheme:</strong> Professional gradient-based palette with accent colors</li>
                        <li><strong>Improved Typography:</strong> Better font pairing and sizing for readability</li>
                        <li><strong>White Space Utilization:</strong> Breathing room between sections for better scanning</li>
                        <li><strong>Visual Storytelling:</strong> Strategic imagery and icon placement</li>
                        <li><strong>Micro-interactions:</strong> Subtle hover effects for improved engagement</li>
                        <li><strong>Consistent Branding:</strong> Unified logo and design elements throughout</li>
